{"tid":2439175,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梅根遭同父異母姊批評「忽視真相」 以抑鬱為藉口對人「用完即棄」","createTime":"2021-03-09T05:11:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T20:23:24.000Z","uid":130626,"like":88,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"23600ce0699f703aa40867bac4da32a382aba5b9","tid":2439175,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:11:07.000Z","msg":"出示舊照片 打破梅根「20年無見」說謊<br />\n56歲的薩曼莎接受娛樂新聞網站《Inside Edition》訪問逐點反擊，她表示︰「我不知道她如何可以說出『我不認識她』和『她只是個小孩』。我們有從小一起生活的照片。她如何可以不認識我。」<br />\n<br />\n她更批評梅根專訪是「完全忽視和刪除真相」，又分享多張兩人在不同年齡的合照，最近一張攝在13年前，2008年薩曼莎的大學畢業禮上兩姊妹合照，駁斥梅根聲稱兩人沒見面20年的說法。<br />\n<br />\n薩曼莎又出示法庭證明，顯示早於1997年12月已經改姓氏，同時展示大學畢業證書上印有姓氏「馬克爾」。<br />\n<br />\n被問到梅根聲稱曾受自殺的想法困擾，薩曼莎坦言不太可憐梅根，更指控對方利用心理健康作為藉口，「抑鬱並不是藉口，把人當成洗碗布一般對待，然後丟棄它」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210309/PJJ2YL6VJFDPVE34LIY276RDNU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210309%2FPJJ2YL6VJFDPVE34LIY276RDNU%2F&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1MhyxUAsmJrpgm%2FsQZzOZZuI0I%3D&h=1f6f8c6c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210309%2FPJJ2YL6VJFDPVE34LIY276RDNU%2F&h=c98d0fdd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210309/PJJ2YL6VJFDPVE34LIY276RDNU/</a>"},{"pid":"72a35b514e7f4aca82ad1869c281bcc72e7c7e99","tid":2439175,"uid":287879,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:15:50.000Z","msg":"群魔亂舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78ef8093a05006da9a1dcba7c16b2313558d119e","tid":2439175,"uid":210669,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:24:44.000Z","msg":"笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大話精黎"},{"pid":"51b5ba6d8f5ed173f693e989c8c943555879be81","tid":2439175,"uid":130626,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"78ef8093a05006da9a1dcba7c16b2313558d119e","tid":2439175,"uid":210669,"lik